l","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"14780f085639278742451c7f123cea2c","url_token":"gen-wo-hui-jiang-nan-ba-33","name":"宋珂琛","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3f5395cbc12eda3bfeed21b49dafc564_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3f5395cbc12eda3bfeed21b49dafc564_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/14780f085639278742451c7f123cea2c","user_type":"people","headline":"2019届高考考生，一切都在学习中","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560624320","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-691ada51cc4364cc589d8cc2f821e235_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545874842,"updated_time":1545874842,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我真的觉得这位同学的这句话有点看不起三百年来全世界数学家的智商\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-96e0bc4879007a456f5d97074e16c091_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2160\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-00e1cbc0deb48ddc840b63b8f12c6bbe_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-96e0bc4879007a456f5d97074e16c091_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='2160'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2160\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-00e1cbc0deb48ddc840b63b8f12c6bbe_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-96e0bc4879007a456f5d97074e16c091_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-96e0bc4879007a456f5d97074e16c091_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560538074,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"365cd503cb53081286b88a01b75e3d5c","url_token":"liu-tao-ming-84","name":"刘涛铭","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/365cd503cb53081286b88a01b75e3d5c","user_type":"people","headline":"钻研物理数学的足球运动员","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560538074","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545854014,"updated_time":1545854014,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e要不等到2019.1.1被找到漏洞之后再来慢慢喷？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是爱憎分明的：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e如果你是民科，那我非常看不起你，\u003c/b\u003e因为我看不起那些自认为智商很高的一般人；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e但如果你是天才，我会十分敬重你，\u003c/b\u003e甚至把你“从被攻击到没人敢再攻击”的过程拍成激动人心的电影来赞扬你！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是实事求是的：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e毛泽东同志曾说过：“没有调查就没有发言权”（你可以理解为“学霸不看题是不会写答案的”）在看清事实真相之前，我不做评论，万一真的是个天才呢？（一个简单的数学思维：“极小”和“0”还是有区别的）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但有些人调查到了很多信息，推测出他证明哥德巴赫猜想的可能性为0，然后再开始攻击他——\u003cb\u003e很好！至少没有像某些人那样没有调查就开喷，\u003c/b\u003e但是你是否知道：民科≈对数学的喜好+一点点知识？如果能给他更多知识是不是也算是培养了一个人才（即使不是爱因斯坦特斯拉那样的巨星天才）\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e是否调查过？是否支持或中立？这两个答案的组合构建了评论区主要的2×3=6类人，\u003c/b\u003e这6类人我最想指责的人是没调查就不支持的人，不管你本人是否有能力，因为你有“不管怎样都看不起别人”的心态。（因为这种人，俗称喷子。）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于调查过，认为高同学没有能力，所以开始嘲笑他的人，我\u003cb\u003e仅仅是呼吁一下\u003c/b\u003e：“每一个物理界的人都希望世界尽可能的多一些科学家（路人就别来打扰物理界的合作氛围了...），所以不如我们善意的教育他，提升他？而不是攻击”毕竟高同学至少有一个难得的优点：他的思想是积极的！他以数学成就为骄傲，而不是能喝多少瓶啤酒...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e至于缺点，很多人会觉得他自大，所以就算是批评，也不要扯上学术内容...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外，如果我是高同学，我也不喜欢那些盲目支持我的人，我会希望大家会在看懂我的思路之后从中立态度变为支持态度（前提是：如果我真的是对的...）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e最后，送上一句某数学家的座右铭：“我决不承认自己是错的，因为我总会是对的；我之所以总会是对的，因为我总会承认自己错了。”\u003c/b\u003e（为了语句听起来更美...这句话被改写得很不符合逻辑...）我只想告诉你人不仅要坚持真理，更要有承认错误的高贵品质。——两者结合，便是\u003cb\u003e目前的科学素养：实事求是。\u003c/b\u003e如果你的理论被推翻了，你会很没面子，我希望你坚持下去，脚踏实地，用一生向大家证明，不是证明你多有能力，而是证明你有这样的素养。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...好了我要睡了真困还好我已经洗完澡了明天还要练深蹲...\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560446749,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"15cba114d649df1ca9793d3ede0c588f","url_token":"geng-geng-50-53-82","name":"耿耿","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-54d96490eacc9bb66f623126a32f3f0a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-54d96490eacc9bb66f623126a32f3f0a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/15cba114d649df1ca9793d3ede0c588f","user_type":"people","headline":"知乎私信功能不太好，想聊天可以添加\n wechat: lin123456zs","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560446749","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545838379,"updated_time":1545838394,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e别说你可以上北大清华了，你还可以让北大上清华\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560420239,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ebff1a8e63b59c1f763148b0eb2f9739","url_token":"shi-yu-1-27","name":"事煜","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-af2ef0f8a8f220055963cc2653260cef_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-af2ef0f8a8f220055963cc2653260cef_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ebff1a8e63b59c1f763148b0eb2f9739","user_type":"people","headline":"学习掌控自己","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560420239","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545836307,"updated_time":1545836307,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e首先回答你的问题。如果你成功证明哥德巴赫猜想且得到学界的认同，不论你的身份如何都能进入最高学府。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其次，像这种验证数学界皇冠猜想的论文不适合发表在知乎这种泛娱乐化app上，应该发表在科研期刊上。大多数普通用户完全看不懂高深的数论证明，俺作为一个农民工，也没读过什么书。闹不清你想干啥？你是把金枝玉露，龙肝凤髓给俺们尝吗，我还是觉得大饼就大葱实在。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560003237,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_pr